(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``If you'd had your choice and say the Irving Thalberg Award or
say the White House, I think I'd stick with this.'' &QL; 
Warren Beatty, recipient of the Irving Thalberg Memorial Award &QL;
</P>
