researched the period well and has a feel for the headiness and yet
the innocence of the times. He provides a fascinating look at the
studio system in its early days, the power, utter crassness and
greed of the early moguls and the limitless possibilities of an
enormous industry still in its infancy.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
