<P>
   TECHNOLOGY
</P>
<P>
   COXNET PTECH _ (EDS: This is the CoxNet PTECH page for the
current week. This layout is available Tuesday after 2 p.m. EST.)
</P>
<P>
   COXNET PTECH 0328 _ A debate over Internet crime pits law
enforcement authorities against civil libertarians. The controversy
pits members of the security establishment against the champions of
privacy and civil liberties. (Glass, Cox Washington Bureau) Art
includes an attractive 4-column color illustration of a thief
