c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Let's start with a supportable thesis, and duly credit a master:
For pure listening satisfaction it's hard to improve on the
seductive intimacy of radio.
</P>
<P>
   From 1956 to 1977, Jean Shepherd held weeknight seminars on
