<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Monday, March 27, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Editors: &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   GENOCIDE-SUSPECT (Laredo, Texas) will not move today on the
Hearst News Service wire.
</P>
<P>
   Hearst News Service/Washington.
</P>
