   _ The National Association for PET Container Resources:
http://www.napcor.com
</P>
<P>
   _ EPA publications on composting:
http://www.epa.gov/epaoswer/non-hw/compost/index.htm
</P>
<P>
   _ ``It's Gotten Rotten,'' a Cornel University film for high
school students on the biology of composting:
http://www.cfe.cornell.edu/compost/IGR.html
</P>
