<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-27 15:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9305 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      03-27 0834
