<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-27 17:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9413 &Cx1f; taf-z
s k BC-ON-LANGUAGE-$ADV02-NY     03-27 1090
