<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-27 19:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9544 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-FRIEDMAN-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      03-27 0756
