   OIL-MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ As the oil ministers met in Vienna,
Austria, there was great concern about whether OPEC would give the
rest of the world a break and do something to restrain soaring oil
prices. So it was nearly 20 years ago, when OPEC met in the fall of
1980. But there are important differences between then and now. By
Floyd Norris.
