a person, double occupancy, from Los Angeles, including air fare,
five nights at the Southern Cross Hotel and a harbor cruise.
Round-trip add-on air fare from New York is $422. Tickets must be
purchased by April 30 for travel between April 17 and Aug. 23.
Other cities in Australia and New Zealand are available.
Reservations: (800) 421-3326. &QL;
